WEBVTT

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:45.400
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:53.439
Meiduo

00:00:53.439 --> 00:00:55.399
This is more precious than anything.

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:58.439
Ah.

00:00:58.439 --> 00:00:58.840
Come here.

00:01:02.359 --> 00:01:03.159
Wen Li.

00:01:03.159 --> 00:01:04.159
Let me introduce you.

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:05.719
This is Gesang Meiduo.

00:01:05.959 --> 00:01:07.719
She is the only one in my heart.

00:01:08.359 --> 00:01:10.200
And the person I will protect for my whole life.

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:16.239
Sorry.

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:17.120
I made you misunderstand.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:18.760
So that's how it is.

00:01:19.799 --> 00:01:21.519
Brother Gao Yuan, you are so fortunate.

00:01:21.719 --> 00:01:22.959
Comrade Gesang Meiduo.

00:01:22.959 --> 00:01:23.560
Hello.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.120
Hello.

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:26.000
I wish you both well.

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:27.760
I'll be waiting for your wedding feast.

00:01:28.519 --> 00:01:29.719
Thank you for your blessing.

00:01:29.719 --> 00:01:30.239
Take care.

00:01:37.359 --> 00:01:38.239
Meiduo.

00:01:38.239 --> 00:01:39.760
I chose to put down roots in Xizang.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:42.200
Partly because of the call of my ideals.

00:01:42.760 --> 00:01:44.239
And partly...

00:01:44.239 --> 00:01:45.560
because it is your homeland.

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.400
We have a shared goal.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.400
I'll be waiting for you in Xizang.

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.000
Mm-hmm.

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:05.439
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:07.480
My heart has followed your footsteps.

00:02:08.159 --> 00:02:10.400
You said putting down roots in Xizang was for your ideals...

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:11.599
and also for me.

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:13.240
I understand.

00:02:13.240 --> 00:02:14.280
Without you...

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.400
without the People's Liberation Army...

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:16.319
Deji and I...

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:18.680
would still be talking livestock in the eyes of serf owners.

00:02:19.159 --> 00:02:20.919
You gave me a new life.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.800
Let me taste liberation.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:26.159
This taste is being able to breathe freely.

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:28.360
It's being able to strive for a shared tomorrow.

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:31.800
And being able to love someone openly and honestly.

00:03:08.599 --> 00:03:09.360
Hey.

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:10.120
Hmm?

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:11.240
Let me ask you.

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:13.560
Why hasn't Balu Yundan come to class?

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:14.919
Today...

00:03:14.919 --> 00:03:16.719
the sun rose from the west.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:19.000
Why are you suddenly concerned about him?

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:20.560
I'm just asking.

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:22.120
He hasn't come to class, right?

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:23.319
As for us...

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:25.879
coming here from a plateau over 4,000 meters high...

00:03:26.759 --> 00:03:29.599
it's inevitable many would have trouble acclimating.

00:03:29.919 --> 00:03:30.960
And get sick because of it.

00:03:31.159 --> 00:03:32.159
I heard...

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:34.719
Balu Yundan seems quite seriously ill.

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.000
He has tuberculosis.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.599
Serves him right.

00:03:37.919 --> 00:03:39.800
I'm a medical assistant now.

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:43.199
Responsible for caring for sick classmates.

00:03:43.199 --> 00:03:44.560
But...

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.080
Are you trying to say...

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.360
if you should go see him?

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.520
Even though he...

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.800
changed a lot after coming to the Public School...

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:57.800
and hasn't bullied me again...

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.439
what he did before...

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:01.360
is unforgivable.

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:04.039
Just let him...

00:04:04.039 --> 00:04:06.000
die from his illness and rot.

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.039
Well...

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:08.280
That's a bit much, isn't it?

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:10.000
I was just joking.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:11.560
Don't take it seriously.

00:04:15.759 --> 00:04:16.920
Cough, cough.

00:04:30.279 --> 00:04:31.600
Deji, why are you here?

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:33.680
Teacher Yu Ling sent me to treat you.

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:35.839
You...

00:04:35.839 --> 00:04:38.279
Are you willing to let me give you a shot?

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:39.399
Willing.

00:04:39.399 --> 00:04:40.800
You can give it however you like.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:47.759
You said it.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.800
Mm-hmm.

00:04:49.519 --> 00:04:50.319
Take off your clothes.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:52.360
I'm still sick...

00:04:53.399 --> 00:04:53.839
That...

00:04:53.839 --> 00:04:54.600
isn't really appropriate.

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:56.360
Just take them off when told.

00:04:56.399 --> 00:04:57.600
Close the door, close it!

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.160
Sit down.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:03.519
Ah!

00:05:03.519 --> 00:05:04.759
Sit down.

00:05:06.959 --> 00:05:08.120
Teacher Yu Ling said...

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.199
a butt shot works best.

00:05:10.199 --> 00:05:11.000
A butt shot?

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:12.000
Go over there.

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:24.720
Hold him down.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.480
Deji.

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:33.000
Why did you come to save me?

00:05:42.959 --> 00:05:45.079
Because it's a doctor's duty.

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:47.120
And also because...

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:50.800
you saved candy for me when we were kids.

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:04.199
You even got whipped by your father for it.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:07.959
You still remember something so long ago?

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.160
Deji.

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.399
I'm sorry.

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.680
I did many bad things before.

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.319
You are so kind...

00:06:21.759 --> 00:06:22.680
and still treat my illness.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:24.399
Thank you.

00:06:24.399 --> 00:06:25.000
Forgive me.

00:06:27.399 --> 00:06:28.680
Who said I forgive you?

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:30.920
I haven't forgiven you.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:32.000
Well, well.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:36.519
You lowly hereditary serf.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:39.000
How dare you enter our noble young master's room?

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.480
What?

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.279
Climbing up to Young Master Yundan?

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.920
Wanting to be the young mistress?

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:45.360
Sangguo Jiamei!

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:46.920
Deji is here to help treat my illness.

00:06:47.079 --> 00:06:48.160
Apologize to her quickly.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.600
I don't need their apology.

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:55.600
I was born a hereditary serf.

00:06:56.959 --> 00:06:59.360
But now, I am the same as you.

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:01.199
I am a student of the Tibetan Public School.

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:02.600
We are equal.

00:07:03.079 --> 00:07:04.759
I came to care for a sick classmate.

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:06.560
You are his friends.

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:08.920
Yet you mock the person helping him here.

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:10.920
Are you even human?

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:12.920
Deji.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:23.680
Fellow students.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:26.279
Today is a special day.

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:28.920
Student Balu Yundan will here...

00:07:29.319 --> 00:07:31.040
offer to Gesang Meiduo...

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:32.879
and the Gesang Deji sisters...

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:36.079
his most sincere apology from the heart.

00:07:59.279 --> 00:08:00.759
Respected

00:08:00.759 --> 00:08:02.120
Gesang Meiduo

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:03.759
and fellow student Gesang Deji,

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.519
In the past,

00:08:05.519 --> 00:08:07.560
there was much unpleasantness between us.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.519
It also had a negative impact on the school.

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:13.000
Today, I want to tell you,

00:08:13.879 --> 00:08:14.879
and tell everyone,

00:08:15.399 --> 00:08:16.959
I reflect on it every day.

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.399
I have deeply realized my mistakes.

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.399
I wish to express three points of sincerity.

00:08:24.519 --> 00:08:25.519
First,

00:08:25.519 --> 00:08:28.120
Regardless of whether we were masters

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:29.199
or servants in the past,

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.519
but now,

00:08:31.519 --> 00:08:32.720
we are classmates,

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:34.679
friends,

00:08:34.679 --> 00:08:35.879
and equals.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:37.600
Second,

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:39.519
I want to learn from you.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.679
To learn from Gesang Meiduo's

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:42.720
positive progressiveness.

00:08:43.559 --> 00:08:45.279
To learn from Gesang Deji's

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:46.320
kindness and tolerance.

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.480
To learn from the activists'

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:50.600
endurance of hardship,

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.679
diligence in study,

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:53.720
and helpful spirit.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:57.559
I will completely abandon old thoughts and ways of life.

00:08:58.559 --> 00:08:59.440
Third,

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.399
I hope you can accept my apology.

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:05.399
I want to become good classmates

00:09:05.399 --> 00:09:06.399
and good friends with you.

00:09:07.799 --> 00:09:09.279
Fine words alone are not enough.

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:13.080
I will prove my resolve through action.

00:09:14.519 --> 00:09:16.320
Please watch my future conduct.

00:09:32.559 --> 00:09:34.279
Respected fellow student Gesang Deji,

00:09:34.919 --> 00:09:37.440
This Khata represents my respect

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:38.159
and my apology to you.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.480
Please accept my apology.